What are some qualities that you would look for in someone you would hire as an assistant?
When hiring an assistant, I would seek out individuals who possess strong organizational skills, excellent communication abilities, and the capacity to work independently while also being a team player. Additionally, it is important to me that they have a positive attitude, are highly motivated, and display reliability in their work habits. Lastly, I would want someone with whom I can establish trust and build a strong professional relationship.
